<A>__{a seedy traveling salesman with badly fitted dentures and a frayed collar has taken the aisle seat next to joe. as he lectures joe on salesmanship, he figures his expenses in a worn leatherette notebook, nervous fingers and eyes unconsciously revealing the extent of his failure.}
